flowchart TD
    GrantCheck([Request replacement options]) --> GrantValid{Grant active and purpose-bound?}
    GrantValid -- No --> ReenrollReject[Reject without account changes]
    GrantValid -- Yes --> ReplacementPrompt[Create grant-bound challenge and run passkey prompt]
    ReplacementPrompt --> ReplacementValid{Attestation and challenge valid?}
    ReplacementValid -- No --> KeepOriginalState[Keep credentials and code unchanged]
    KeepOriginalState -->|Retry while authorization remains valid| ReplacementPrompt
    ReplacementValid -- Yes --> BeginCompletion[Begin immediate completion transaction]
    BeginCompletion --> RecheckState{Grant, transaction, code, and user still match?}
    RecheckState -- No --> RollbackCompletion[Rollback every change]
    RecheckState -- Yes --> InsertReplacement[Insert active replacement credential]
    InsertReplacement --> ConsumeGrant[Consume grant and complete transaction]
    ConsumeGrant --> RevokeLost[Revoke reported lost credential]
    RevokeLost --> RedeemAndRotate[Redeem old code and store new code digest]
    RedeemAndRotate --> WriteNotifications[Write recovery notification outbox]
    WriteNotifications --> CommitCompletion[Commit all state changes]
    CommitCompletion --> CompletionReceipt[Return statuses and new code once]
    CompletionReceipt --> ReplacementSignIn[Run normal passkey Authentication]
    ReplacementSignIn --> ReplacementWorks{Replacement assertion valid?}
    ReplacementWorks -- Yes --> RecoveryProven([Recovery complete and signed in])
    ReplacementWorks -- No --> PostRecoveryFailure[Show generic sign-in failure]
